# Step 1: Problem Statement & Personal Role

## Problem Statement
Customers need a secure and user-friendly online platform to browse products, manage purchases, track orders, and access personalized shopping experiences. Administrators need efficient tools to manage products, users, inventory, orders, and transactions.

## Personal Role
As the sole developer, I am responsible for:

- Frontend Development
- Backend Development
- Database Design
- Authentication Implementation
- API Development
- Testing & Debugging
- Deployment
- System Maintenance

